00:12:07.710 --> 00:12:10.940
So yes the central bank
can buy some of the money

00:12:10.940 --> 00:12:14.570
or sell some of the money
which affects the supply

00:12:14.570 --> 00:12:16.820
and thus affects the price.

00:12:16.820 --> 00:12:20.660
So open market operations
effectively affects

00:12:20.660 --> 00:12:22.190
