00:29:04.660 --> 00:29:10.600
It's human-- it's who we are.

00:29:10.600 --> 00:29:13.330
So my father had a small
business in Baltimore.

00:29:13.330 --> 00:29:15.580
He never had more
than 30 employees.

00:29:15.580 --> 00:29:20.890
