him out on Monday.

00:29:26.670 --> 00:29:29.930
His employees might give him
another week or two-- hey, Sam!

00:29:29.930 --> 00:29:32.370
My dad's name is Sam.

00:29:32.370 --> 00:29:34.440
We'll give Mr. Sam another week.

00:29:34.440 --> 00:29:38.390
But two or three weeks later,
they would have all quit.

00:29:38.390 --> 00:29:44.570
But the banks, so large, so
tied into their economies--

00:29:44.570 --> 00:29:46.760
for many decades.

00:29:46.760 --> 00:29:49.460
2008 wasn't the only time.

00:29:49.460 --> 00:29:51.110
The sovereign steps in.

00:29:51.110 --> 00:29:53.030
The central bank steps in.

00:29:53.030 --> 00:29:54.590
So Kelly, the answer
to your question

00:29:54.590 --> 00:29:58.760
