00:30:00.770 --> 00:30:03.410
They still have very
real tools to be

00:30:03.410 --> 00:30:05.780
the firefighter in the
middle of a raging fire,

00:30:05.780 --> 00:30:08.870
but they're a little
bit more constrained.

00:30:08.870 --> 00:30:11.390
We as a society spoke through
our Congress and said,

00:30:11.390 --> 00:30:14.490
we don't want bailouts.

00:30:14.490 --> 00:30:17.430
But in the midst of the
next crisis, some Treasury

00:30:17.430 --> 00:30:19.710
Secretary, and some
Federal Reserve chair,

00:30:19.710 --> 00:30:23.280
and maybe some president,
will be testing the limits

00:30:23.280 --> 00:30:25.760
of those statutory authorities.

00:30:25.760 --> 00:30:28.287
And they might be knocking on
the doors of Congress again.

