00:36:00.690 --> 00:36:05.040
I think wide adoption in any
country you'd have to address,

00:36:05.040 --> 00:36:07.860
will the government
accept it for taxes?

00:36:07.860 --> 00:36:11.175
Will the government say it's
accepted as legal tender?

00:36:11.175 --> 00:36:16.370
And until and
unless that happens,

00:36:16.370 --> 00:36:18.440
usually it wouldn't
have wide adoption,

00:36:18.440 --> 00:36:20.390
even in a country
