And in the US, it was called
the free banking area.

00:37:05.230 --> 00:37:08.110
Andrew Jackson was the seventh
president of the United States,

00:37:08.110 --> 00:37:11.385
and he really didn't
like a central bank.

00:37:11.385 --> 00:37:13.900
It was called the second
bank of the United States,

00:37:13.900 --> 00:37:18.810
